N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 187.4 - Daily air components determination; oxygen percentage regulated

State Regulations

Each owner or operator shall make the required air
components determinations daily. The percent of oxygen shall be reduced to five
percent within 20 days after date of sealing. Notes
